{"tid":1560060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（立場新聞專訪）「香港之歌」誕生？　《願榮光歸香港》創作人：音樂是凝聚人心最強武器","createTime":"2019-09-11T05:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:47:34.000Z","uid":36494,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a535bf4e9395f0ae48b31e9704c446d9a2823173","tid":1560060,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:23:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%98%AF%E5%87%9D%E8%81%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%2594%259F-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2587%259D%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=45ebeac9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%2594%259F-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2587%259D%25E8%2581%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%2F&h=9f0d9d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%8C-%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%98%AF%E5%87%9D%E8%81%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8/</a><br />\n<br />\n今期流行：「何以，這土地淚再流 &hellip; 」<br />\n<br />\n9 月 10 日，《願榮光歸香港》一曲響遍全港各區。香港足球代表隊在大球場迎戰伊朗，球證鳴笛開賽，看台上球迷隨即合唱，如唱國歌；中場休息大家築成人鏈，再唱；球賽結束，魚貫散場之時，繼續唱，走到銅鑼灣鬧市，仍在唱。<br />\n<br />\n同一晚，繼沙田、太古後，黃大仙、屯門、馬鞍山、旺角、葵芳、將軍澳、上水、觀塘，都有上千市民響應號召，齊集區內商場，眼望歌詞，一同合唱。埸面極其墟冚。一時之間，《願榮光歸香港》彷彿成為一首「香港之歌」。<br />\n<br />\n這首歌是如何誕生的？<br />\n<br />\n「香港人需要有 power、能凝聚人心的歌。」T 接受《立場新聞》專訪時說，希望《願榮光歸香港》能成為這樣的一首歌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文好長，自己入去link睇"},{"pid":"0e64541126fb030dca3f3764a075c2b3f542c2b2","tid":1560060,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"有人覺得，在社運現場唱歌是「左膠」所為，無實質意義，T 不太認同。寫《願榮光》之前，他搜集過不少資料，「自古以來的士兵都有好多軍歌，打緊仗時現場太嘈，梗係唔會唱；但情況好惡劣，又或平時消磨下時間，都會唱下軍歌，激勵士氣。」<br />\n<br />\n因此他嘗試為香港抗爭者創作這首歌，「要可以激勵士氣，感染人心嘅。」"},{"pid":"e80cd56ac26b5595317bfec54213b19f8ff2d333","tid":1560060,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"「希望香港變回光榮城市」<br />\n<br />\n有了旋律，就寫歌詞。T 最先想好的，當然又是全曲最後一句，「我願榮光歸香港」。<br />\n<br />\n「現在太多不公義的情況。大家以為香港是個繁榮安定、好光榮的城市。但原來一直揭露下去，原來唔係嘅 &hellip; 」<br />\n<br />\n所以「我願榮光歸香港」有兩層意思，第一是展望未來，「希望香港可變返一個大家心目中的光榮、榮耀的城市」，第二是指香港人「願意將個人的榮耀和光榮歸予香港」。<br />\n<br />\n有些人看到歌名中的「榮光」二字，以為歌曲有宗教意味，T 笑言自己不是教徒，而「榮光」既是基督教常用詞彙，其實也曾出自李白（「方將延榮光於後昆，軼玄風於邃古。」《大獵賦》）、魯迅（「他們的國粹，既然這樣有榮光，他們自然也有榮光了！」 《熱風 &middot; 隨感錄三十八》），共通點是都有「光榮」、「光采」之意。"},{"pid":"b0c697a05837740dce0643b4c0d062fe4e771c27","tid":1560060,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為左殤台個牌為左碗飯，童星老監馮生都要做奶共狗鳥！！！<br />\n<br />\n為紀念燒死林彬而起嘅18樓C座，狗馮既係老監亦負責主要角色，啱啱居然勁做維撚狗，幫狗政Spin話831死人只係街邊八婆鳩吹出黎，又吹香港咁大城市死幾個人點會遮得到！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩嘩嘩！！我愈聽愈以為轉左俾Mei西監製添！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>疑點1: </ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n光明正大點解要cap圖唔直接放片？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點2: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解Cap既所有圖都唔見畜聾打人，直播又會見到？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點3: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁撚簡單既事點解要封站兩日？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><strong>疑點4: </strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n連721都唔會4個部門一齊見記者，點解831會？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我依家信太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a112e01686f1b26a38e67c158ceb0587cb72182a","tid":1560060,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"狂LOOP洗腦中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mq_wgL0VcEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dmq_wgL0VcEA&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=c170c89f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mq_wgL0VcEA</a>"},{"pid":"8998852a7968a318d7ad3044f67fc083abe6fa70","tid":1560060,"uid":1874,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"btw，熱狗好憎呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都彈呢首歌啲詞乜乜物物，<br />\n覺得佢地首私怨到爆嘅《城邦會戰勝歸