160%2Femojipedia%2F181%2Fwhite-heart_1f90d.png&h=a233330f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬鏡華水晶心獎<br />\n頒發給T和其他用自己的心去反映人世間最美的人<br />\nCrystal Heart Award<br />\nAwarded to T and those who uses their hearts to reflect the most beautiful things in humanity</div></blockquote>"}]}